{"tid":1686513,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【1 1 . 2 抗 暴 物 資 】 香 港 人 既 物 資 站， 物 資 任 你 黎 攞 ！！！！！！！！！！！！！","createTime":"2019-11-01T07:28:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-01T13:38:53.000Z","uid":28105,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"d12cc998cf555388306f59fdf27e3c8b0a18c877","tid":1686513,"uid":28105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-01T07:28:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>⚠️《多元化》物資站⚠️</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">幫手推呀，要令每一位手足出到黎都要有足夠裝備生存<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>TG Channel:<a href=\"https://t.me/Peaceandlovehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FPeaceandlovehk&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=9bf09c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Peaceandlovehk</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Instagram:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/peaceandlovehk?igshid=17gvlktg6vz6b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fpeaceandlovehk%3Figshid%3D17gvlktg6vz6b&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=58923567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/peaceandlovehk?igshid=17gvlktg6vz6b</a></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Facebook:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Peaceandlovehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPeaceandlovehk&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=3ecaeed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Peaceandlovehk</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/tyUtfpQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtyUtfpQ.jpg&h=c4e9b63d&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S1niCDb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS1niCDb.jpg&h=5afc30f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9UdUVpS.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9UdUVpS.jpg&h=f9266ca0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">自612開始與前線風雨同路，直到現在物資義工仍在堅守崗位，每次都會出來支援💪🏻。十月一日我們亦無懼tg在前線派發物資👷🏻&zwj;♂️，我們的義工團中有文宣，影音，Fa隊，家長隊，哨兵</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\"><br />\n‼️我們一直低調行蹤，以保證各義工及手足安全，做到支持前線之餘亦不流血、不送頭！ .<br />\n<br />\n所有物資歡迎各位手足黎任攞‼️‼️‼️</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">日期 : 11月2日<br />\n地點 :  遮打，愛丁堡(兩個物資站)<br />\n時間：17:00集會開始(義工15:30到達)</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">☎️聯絡人TG:<br />\n@TomiMe(遮打)<br />\n@bearbearbb(遮打)<br />\n@wt7usy(愛丁堡)<br />\n@momo111hk(愛丁堡)</span></span><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">‼當天約了拎福袋小朋友或捐贈物資既家長請聯絡admin約時間交收，以保障義工，家長，小朋友安全🙇🏻&zwj;♀🙇🏻&zwj;♀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n保護裝備⛑🥽<br />\n🆘濾咀6200/6800/7502Q<br />\n🆘罐60926/60928<br />\n🆘氣密眼罩40653<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n❌🈲攻擊性武器🈲❌<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n以下物品可以在場內交收：<br />\n✅大量摺紙(遮打收)🙏<br />\n✅口罩(黑色，普通都ok)<br />\n✅乾糧(餅，蛋糕仔，能量棒)<br />\n✅退熱貼，洗手液，濕紙巾.<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足生活飯卷💰<br />\n💵八達通<br />\n💵惠康/百佳超市卷(買日常用品)<br />\n💵KFC/McDonald&rsquo;s/大家樂<br />\n💵鴻福堂現金卷/涼茶卷/湯卷<br />\n💵健康工坊涼茶卷/湯卷 💵八達通<br />\n💵唐記飯卷<br />\n💵書卷/衫褲鞋禮品卡<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">🚸因為現時處於長期抗爭，物資消耗較快，所以物資會定期進行收集，家長有任何物資都可以捐畀我哋，以提供前線人員進行替換🙇🏻&zwj;♀🙇🏻&zwj;♀</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n😊😊查詢詳情可訂閲《多元化》Channel: <br />\n⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️⬇️<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>TG Channel:<a href=\"https://t.me/Peaceandlovehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2FPeaceandlovehk&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=9bf09c8c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/Peaceandlovehk</a></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">Instagram:<a href=\"https://instagram.com/peaceandlovehk?igshid=17gvlktg6vz6b\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fpeaceandlovehk%3Figshid%3D17gvlktg6vz6b&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=58923567\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/peaceandlovehk?igshid=17gvlktg6vz6b</a></span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>Facebook:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Peaceandlovehk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPeaceandlovehk&d=rhNKtzo6pyhm84ltIFKzvG7D9zYHOB9IQ%2BPXuKXaEI4%3D&h=3ecaeed4\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/Peaceandlovehk</a></strong></span></span><br />\n⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️⬆️<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>最後萬分感謝大家的支持！ 香港人加油！ 香港人&middot; 反抗！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\"><strong>香港人加油💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻💪🏻</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">#光復香港時代革命</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">#五大訴求缺一不可</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">不流血 不受傷 不被捕 <br />\n不分化 不篤灰 不割蓆</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: purple;\">#好人一生平安</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mqNKyiN.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmqNKyiN.gif&h=8a99dcd4&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5857f0def1a894855c53466b1368e548b9